## 13. Non‑Reversal Clauses

The following ordering and priorities are non‑reversible and non‑negotiable under this License: [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_e4057470-7756-497e-a75f-b79d6abfc921/401da9a6-eab9-4d94-a506-defca922f58b/collaboration-channels-for-sha-5MJHPghkRGCgdiLq7V62Ag.md)

- (a) Evidence spine first: Research‑Turn / Neural Rope logging MUST precede complex automation or asset sharing.  
- (b) Neurorights outer layer: The neurorights envelope MUST remain the universal interface contract for all platforms and kernels.  
- (c) RoH ≤ 0.3 as supreme governor: No governance, incentive, or authorship rule may override the RoH ceiling.

Any attempt to invert these priorities is void.

